  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "同名の漫画を基にしています。漫画の第12巻までの内容を基にしており、オリジナルのイベントも含まれています。主人公の牧野つくしが主役となり、彼の学校の生徒たちとの親密な関係を築いていきます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Hana Yori Dango: Another Love Story is a Game Boy Color released in 2001.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Makino Tsukushi: a girl who comes from a poor family just wants to get through her 2 last years at Eitoku Gakuen, quietly. But once she makes herself known by standing up for her friend to the F4, the 4 most popular, powerful and rich boys at the school. She gets the red card: F4's way of a \"Declaration of War\". But when she doesnt let herself be beaten by them and is starting to fall for one of the F4; Hanazawa Rui. She starts to see that there is more than meets the eye...",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
  ],
